    "updated_at": "2017-05-17T21:52:20Z",
    "body": "So something like this should work currently:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar buffer = new ArrayBuffer(8);\r\nconst Buffer = require('buffer').Buffer;\r\nipcRenderer.send('sendData', {\r\n   data: Buffer.from(buffer)\r\n});\r\n```"
